data.text: #ThisIsUs What an layered and emotional episode !!! Jack & Rebecca were ❤️ But my God @justinhartley Wow , he has his dad in him in so many ways !! This show has my heart forever . Playing Invisible Ink on repeat now @SiddKhoslaMusic @TheMandyMoore 👏

#ThisIsUs inspires me to be good , to want good in others & to remember no matter what it all eventually falls into place ❤️There isn’t any fiction/non-fiction which has EVER affected me so much !Am absolutely consumed&invested in the Pearson’s😊 14 days wait though is killing😭

Jack would be so proud of his Big 3 , can see him beaming 😇 Jack & Randall, Jack&Rebecca , Kevin & Randall, Kate & Rebecca , Deja & Beth , Kevin & Zoey , Kate & Toby , Randall & Beth !! Boy oh Boy all these moments were heart warming ❤️ #ThisIsUs @Dan_Fogelman @ThisIsUsWriters
